'From Squeak2.8 of 30 June 2000 [No updates present.] on 18 September 2000 at 3:18:04 pm'!"Change Set:		HashFixDate:			18 September 2000Author:			Andres ValloudFix the new hash for SequenceableCollections so that it never overflows. It rarely occurs, but it should never happen"!!LargePositiveInteger methodsFor: 'bit manipulation' stamp: 'SqR 9/18/2000 15:17'!hashMultiply	"Truncate to 28 bits and try again"	^(self bitAnd: 16rFFFFFFF) hashMultiply! !